'''Tetris'''
#{{computing}} an electronic [[game]] in which [[falling]] [[tetromino]]es must be manipulated to form complete lines

===Verb===
# To manipulate a group of objects so as to fit into a pre-defined space in the most efficient and/or desirable manner possible.
#* It took me three hours to tetris my furniture after purchasing a new mahogany dresser.
#* After extensive tetrising Cam and Emily managed to fit all of their worldly posessions into the trunk of their Civic.